System Insets Handling

ViewCompat.setOnApplyWindowInsetsListener(grid) { view, insets ->
    val systemBars = insets.getInsets(WindowInsetsCompat.Type.systemBars())

    view.setPadding(
        systemBars.left,
        systemBars.top,
        systemBars.right,
        systemBars.bottom
    )
    insets
}

Purpose:
- Prevents overlap with status bar and navigation gestures
- Ensures UI remains usable on all devices

App Launch System

val intent = packageManager.getLaunchIntentForPackage(packageName)

if (intent == null) {
    Toast.makeText(this, "Can't launch $packageName", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()
    return
}

startActivity(intent)

Behaviour:
- Safely resolves app launch intent
- Prevents crashes if app is not launchable
- Launches external applications via system

